steps to install:
------------------

1. upload files in root/* to your <web_root>/
2. open install.xml in your local webbrowser
3. follow instructions in your webbrowser for editing files in your <web_root>
4. run http://yoursitename.com/install.php for some more settings to be added
5. remove http://yoursitename.com/install.php or change its permissions to 000
